Q3/- What is the difference between WebApplication and Web-services?

Answer:- WebApplication generates the view page where as Wev-service generates the 
         raw data.
         
         View page cannot be reused but raw data can be used inside any other webApplication or any 
         other type of application developed in any technology.
         
         WebApplication generates a html response while webServices can generate dynamic result
         as raw data(json,xml,text);